snippet: Atletico Madrid coach Diego Simeone again expects a clash of football styles when his side visit Barcelona in the quarter-finals of the Champions League on Tuesday....

headline.print_headline: Atletico Will Look to Impose Own Style on Barca-Simeone
headline.main: Atletico Will Look to Impose Own Style on Barca-Simeone

lead_paragraph: Atletico Madrid coach Diego Simeone again expects a clash of football styles when his side visit Barcelona in the quarter-finals of the Champions League on Tuesday.
